-- Schaeffler Says She `Can't Imagine' Her Company Without Family Ownership
-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 2010-12-10T14:16:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-10/schaeffler-says-she-can-t-imagine-her-company-without-family-ownership.html
Schaeffler Group owner Maria-
Elisabeth Schaeffler said she “can’t imagine” the company
without family ownership and that the future with Continental AG
will be “positive.” She was speaking at a business congress in
Hamburg today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
